---
import Container from "./Container.astro";
---

<section>
    <Container>
        <div class="p-[--card-padding] overflow-hidden lg:aspect-video flex rounded-[--card-border-radius] bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-purple-50 dark:from-indigo-950/30 dark:to-purple-950/30">
            <div class="max-w-4xl w-full h-fit m-auto space-y-12">
                <img src="/lulla-app-screenshot.webp" alt="Lulla app interface showing sleep tracking and CBT-I modules" loading="lazy" width="2481" height="1626">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-12 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-12 max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-gray-950 dark:text-white text-2xl font-semibold">Science-backed approach to better sleep</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Lulla uses <span class="text-gray-950 dark:text-white font-medium">Cognitive Behavioral Therapy for Insomnia (CBT-I)</span>, the gold standard treatment recommended by sleep specialists and proven more effective than sleep medications.</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Our self-guided program adapts to your schedule, helping you identify and change thoughts and behaviors that interfere with sleep.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Container>
</section>